PESHAWAR, Apr 27 (APP):The Federal Government had approved a special financial package for the families of the victims of the CTD Police Station, Kabal tragedy, a Central Police Office (CPO) Peshawar press release said on Thursday.
Under the package, the families of martyred CTD personnel would be given Rs 2 million each while the injured would get Rs 0.5 million each.
